1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,237
=Episode 21=

3
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:54,240
Dear friends,

4
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:56,600
thank you all for coming

5
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:58,119
to Mr. Ye and Ms. Qin's wedding.

6
00:00:58,119 --> 00:00:59,560
What's so special about Ye Chen?

7
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:01,759
Why does everyone want
to marry their daughter to him?

8
00:01:02,039 --> 00:01:03,280
Don't you know?

9
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,500
Ye Chen isn't an ordinary man.

10
00:01:04,719 --> 00:01:05,759
He's a master.

11
00:01:05,759 --> 00:01:06,990
The kind who can summon storms.

12
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,200
Qin Gang really

13
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:09,719
struck gold this time.

14
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:11,359
Now,

15
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:13,120
let's give a wam round of applause

16
00:01:13,120 --> 00:01:14,959
for the bride of today.

17
00:01:20,879 --> 00:01:22,239
Why is it her?

18
00:01:28,712 --> 00:01:30,040
What's going on?

19
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:31,280
What's this?

20
00:01:37,340 --> 00:01:41,620
♪How long since I held your hand♪

21
00:01:45,260 --> 00:01:49,340
♪While we talked
about the past and future♪

22
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:57,380
♪How long since we asked
how each other were♪

23
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,439
Ye Chen,

24
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:02,079
just two days ago,

25
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:06,040
you swore to me
that no matter who they are,

26
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:08,000
your heart belonged only to me.

27
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,120
Even though our marriage was fake,

28
00:02:13,275 --> 00:02:14,660
But your feelings for me were real

29
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,599
after everything we've been though.

30
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:19,800
You said

31
00:02:20,175 --> 00:02:21,335
no matter who you became,

32
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:24,240
your feelings for me would never change.

33
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,080
Churan.

34
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:29,879
You asked me to trust you, and I did.

35
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:31,790
But what about you?

36
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,120
Ye Chen,

37
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,319
do you still remember

38
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,719
when Grandma tied you up

39
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,360
and forced you to marry me?

40
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:43,240
At first, I had no faith
in our marriage.

41
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,560
I thought you only wanted money.

42
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:50,120
But you respect me and took care of me.

43
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,840
This past year

44
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,319
has been the happiest time of my life.

45
00:02:56,825 --> 00:02:58,658
When they forced me
to marry Zhang Wenhao,

46
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,759
You shameless thing!

47
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,560
you endured humiliation

48
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:03,599
and ridicule

49
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,887
and still stood by side to protect me.

50
00:03:07,437 --> 00:03:09,360
I'll work hard for that goal!

51
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,787
You helped me become chairperson

52
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,159
to fulfill Grandpa's wish.

53
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,199
For me,

54
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,759
you risked your life again and again.

55
00:03:22,662 --> 00:03:24,257
But when you were surrounded by enemies

56
00:03:24,837 --> 00:03:26,305
and faced with death,

57
00:03:26,759 --> 00:03:28,560
why can't you trust

58
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,759
that I can also

59
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,319
stand by your side firmly?

60
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,759
I know everything now.

61
00:03:39,199 --> 00:03:41,479
No matter how dangerous
the road ahead may be,

62
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,759
I want to walk it with you.

63
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,680
No matter who you become,

64
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,080
I will never leave you.

65
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:53,080
Whether in life or in death,

66
00:03:55,650 --> 00:03:57,477
I'll stay with you forever.

67
00:04:01,479 --> 00:04:02,199
Honey,

68
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,000
I love you.

69
00:04:08,050 --> 00:04:12,775
♪We kept running, forgot to look back♪

70
00:04:13,719 --> 00:04:14,400
Will...

71
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,759
you marry me?

72
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:29,060
♪Going with the flow,
too afraid to speak♪

73
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,199
Silly girl,

74
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,519
how could I possibly refuse?

75
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:42,519
♪It's been so long,
but I still remember♪

76
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,920
But I should be the one

77
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,319
doing this.

78
00:04:51,925 --> 00:04:54,075
♪The rain echoes my longing♪

79
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:55,875
♪Ticking on until the dawn♪

80
00:04:55,937 --> 00:04:59,460
♪Again and again
it reminds my heart of you♪

81
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,360
Churan,

82
00:05:01,400 --> 00:05:03,400
♪Waiting without end♪

83
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:04,800
will you marry me?

84
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,519
I do.

85
00:05:08,712 --> 00:05:12,387
♪My eyes flicker between light and dark♪

86
00:05:12,537 --> 00:05:15,412
♪Only because of you
they change like the weather♪

87
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:19,112
♪Tears drift low through the air
for no reason♪

88
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:22,050
♪Falling, one stubborn drop♪

89
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,275
♪The rain echoes my longing♪

90
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:26,859
♪Ticking on until the dawn♪

91
00:05:26,860 --> 00:05:30,660
♪Again and again
it reminds my heart of you♪

92
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:32,460
♪Hope makes you sink deeper♪

93
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:34,420
♪Waiting without end♪

94
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:38,260
♪Yet I never see the end
of this downpour♪

95
00:05:38,260 --> 00:05:39,940
♪The rain echoes my longing♪

96
00:05:39,940 --> 00:05:41,820
♪Ticking on until the dawn♪
(Happy Wedding)

97
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:45,460
♪Again and again
it reminds my heart of you♪

98
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:47,420
♪Can you hear the voice of my heart?♪

99
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:49,300
♪My longing floods the city♪

100
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:51,900
♪Yet I can’t bear to soak you
as you look into my eyes♪

101
00:05:51,959 --> 00:05:53,040
Master, Madam,

102
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,920
this is so touching.

103
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,680
Your ceremony's over.

104
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:59,279
Can I start my ceremony too?

105
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,959
What ceremony?

106
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,480
I can promise you,

107
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,519
but I need you to help me
with something.

108
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,120
What do you need?

109
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,240
I'll do anything.

110
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:11,839
Tomorrow,

111
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,199
you are to find Churan.

112
00:06:18,639 --> 00:06:19,360
(Happy Wedding)
Look!

113
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,110
(Apprenticeship Ceremony
Master: Ye Chen, Disciple: Qin Aoxue)

114
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,639
Congratulations.

115
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:22,600
Chen,

116
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:26,279
are you happy with today's arrangement?

117
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:27,990
Thank you for making it happen, Mr. Qin.

118
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,279
Everything right here

119
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:32,199
is the best choice for me.

120
00:06:32,879 --> 00:06:35,040
The heavens bear witness, I, Qin Aoxue,

121
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:36,800
officially take Ye Chen as my master.

122
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:38,839
Master,

123
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,879
please have some tea.

124
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:49,160
Madam, your tea.

125
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:56,639
Madam, I'll definitely protect you
from now on.

126
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,199
If anyone dares bully you,

127
00:06:58,199 --> 00:06:59,079
I'll beat them up.

128
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:01,079
I hereby announce

129
00:07:01,439 --> 00:07:02,480
that starting today

130
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:05,079
Ye Chen is my master!

131
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,160
- Yay!
- Great!

132
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,399
How did you know who I was?

133
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,639
That day,

134
00:07:13,079 --> 00:07:14,600
I was waiting for you in the garden.

135
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,560
You never came,

136
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,920
but Wang Dongxue did.

137
00:07:21,279 --> 00:07:21,920
Ms. Xiao,

138
00:07:23,839 --> 00:07:24,959
Mr. Tang wants to see you.

139
00:07:29,262 --> 00:07:32,700
(The Ye Family's Business Empire)

140
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,399
Ms. Xiao,

141
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,560
now you know Ye Chen's true identity.

142
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,199
If you really love him,

143
00:07:48,639 --> 00:07:49,959
I hope you'll understand him.

144
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,680
Leave him,

145
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,079
so he can marry Qin Aoxue.

146
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:54,519
Only then

147
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,480
can he get the formula

148
00:07:56,687 --> 00:07:58,524
and find the murderer
who killed Madam Li

149
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,319
to fulfill his late parents' last wish.

150
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:05,920
This...

151
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,480
is also for your own good.

152
00:08:08,879 --> 00:08:10,560
I'm sure Ye Chen wouldn't want you

153
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:12,839
to fall into the same danger
as Madan Li.

154
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,519
I'm sorry,

155
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,319
Churan.

156
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,519
I kept it from you

157
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,199
to not drag you into this.

158
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,680
I'm not scared.

159
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,839
Silly.

160
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:28,199
We're on the same boat.

161
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,560
Don't even think about pushing me away.

162
00:08:32,040 --> 00:08:32,839
Then

163
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,959
what about our contract?

164
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,279
You mean this?

165
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,559
Wait, Churan.

166
00:08:53,519 --> 00:08:54,559
Do you still need

167
00:08:54,879 --> 00:08:56,000
a contract between us?

168
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,550
No need.

169
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,039
Not at all.

170
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,178
We're legally married anyway.

171
00:09:03,679 --> 00:09:04,200
Well.

172
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:06,300
Since we're already legally married,

173
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:07,480
shall we

174
00:09:07,962 --> 00:09:09,262
fulfill some marital duties?

175
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:31,559
Stop it.

176
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:32,200
Let me listen.

177
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,600
Why are you listening in?

178
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,837
What's going on?

179
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,399
Why did they get married again?

180
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,679
I need to ask them.

181
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:38,840
C... Come back.

182
00:09:39,812 --> 00:09:40,960
Just let them be.

183
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,200
As long as they're happy.

184
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:44,080
Why make such a fuss every day?

185
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:44,990
Always making a scene.

186
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:47,200
Can't they just live life peacefully?

187
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:49,880
If you can keep yourself steady,
that's better than anything.

188
00:09:53,159 --> 00:09:57,279
I've noticed you've been getting
pretty bold with me lately.

189
00:09:57,679 --> 00:09:58,559
N... No.

190
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,240
Let me show you something nice.

191
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,039
You like it?

192
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,159
It's for me?

193
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,519
You've suffered a lot

194
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:10,919
staying with me over the years.

195
00:10:11,770 --> 00:10:13,039
I should show some appreciation.

196
00:10:13,399 --> 00:10:14,080
Put it on.

197
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:20,919
Life has been tough.

198
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:22,399
But when I think

199
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:25,480
of Qian Hongyan's
expression when I show her

200
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,519
this necklace,

201
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,399
suddenly it doesn't feel bitter anymore.

202
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:32,120
Our life

203
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,360
is getting better.

204
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:35,480
I'll see if they

205
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,200
ever dare bully us again.

206
00:10:42,159 --> 00:10:44,279
Qin Gang wanted
to marry Qin Aoxue to Ye Chen.

207
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,679
He probably found out
about Ye Chen's identity.

208
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,759
But Ye Chen refused.

209
00:10:51,090 --> 00:10:53,360
So the engagement turned
into an apprenticeship ceremony.

210
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,039
But don't worry.

211
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,879
I've made the arrangements.

212
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:00,880
We've watched the show for long enough.

213
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:03,639
It's time to step on the stage.

214
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,600
This is for your safety,

215
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:11,039
Mrs. Ye's safety,

216
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:13,200
and the legacy your parents left behind.

217
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,870
Victory isn't...

218
00:11:14,879 --> 00:11:15,595
I told you.

219
00:11:15,622 --> 00:11:17,035
I don't want to hear your nagging.

220
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,159
You better remember

221
00:11:19,159 --> 00:11:20,519
every word I've said!

222
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,879
Everything you've said,

223
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,519
I keep in my heart.

224
00:11:26,050 --> 00:11:26,851
However,

225
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,000
if you don't like to hear me,

226
00:11:30,850 --> 00:11:31,800
I'll keep quiet.

227
00:11:34,325 --> 00:11:36,919
Mr. Tang, Mr. Ye,
something happened with the Qin family.

228
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:39,919
Recently,

229
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:42,280
the city's well-known pharma company,
Huaying Pharma,

230
00:11:42,290 --> 00:11:43,799
has been caught in a public scandal.

231
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:45,879
Their newly launched,
Ninefold True Essence Pill ,

232
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:48,039
has been exposed
for serious quality issues.

233
00:11:48,279 --> 00:11:50,137
Many suffered severe adverse reactions

234
00:11:50,175 --> 00:11:51,974
after taking it

235
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,000
which has sparked
widespread public concern.

236
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,087
They're suffered down-limit streaks.

237
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:57,759
Mr. Ye,

238
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,960
this is what I was worried about.

239
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:02,320
The people eyeing
the formula is dangerous.

240
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:03,960
If we don't act soon,

241
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,759
they might gain the upper hand.

242
00:12:06,025 --> 00:12:07,357
This is what I want to see.

243
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,840
If we don't release some bait,

244
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,537
how will the predator come out?

245
00:12:12,650 --> 00:12:14,279
I can use this chance to see if Qin Gang

246
00:12:14,279 --> 00:12:15,737
is worth Dad's trust.

247
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,480
Oh right, Tang Sihai.

248
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:22,259
I'm warning you one last time.

249
00:12:22,812 --> 00:12:24,080
Don't touch Qin Gang.

250
00:12:24,650 --> 00:12:26,159
To subdue the enemy without fighting

251
00:12:26,190 --> 00:12:27,279
is the supreme excellence.

252
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:29,990
Just retrieving the formula
is far from enough.

253
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,480
I will reclaim anyone

254
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:33,562
who was loyal to my father.

255
00:12:56,637 --> 00:12:59,125
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

256
00:12:59,212 --> 00:13:02,965
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

257
00:13:03,425 --> 00:13:08,362
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

258
00:13:08,525 --> 00:13:10,812
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

259
00:13:11,125 --> 00:13:13,805
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

260
00:13:14,875 --> 00:13:17,500
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

261
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:20,812
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

262
00:13:21,012 --> 00:13:24,062
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

263
00:13:24,175 --> 00:13:27,137
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

264
00:13:27,405 --> 00:13:30,562
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

265
00:13:30,787 --> 00:13:34,537
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

266
00:13:34,537 --> 00:13:37,400
♪I belong to no one♪

267
00:13:37,462 --> 00:13:40,912
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

268
00:13:40,912 --> 00:13:43,587
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

269
00:13:43,587 --> 00:13:49,925
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
